<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4525863>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 1. — A, Distribution of the species of Emphania (Emphania erichsoni n. sp.could not be localized due to insufficient label information “Madagascar”),the habitus of the type species E.metallica (Blanchard,1850) is shown (not scaled) in upper left corner;B-D, E. metallica (Blanchard, 1850) (lectotype); E-G, E. lacroixi n. sp. (holotype); B, E, aedeagus, left side lateral views; C, F, aedeagus, dorsal views; D, G, aedeagus, right side lateral views. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4525863/files/figure.png" .

